{"SEMIVERTICILLATE":[{"def":"Partially verticillate.","pos":""}],"SEMIVIF":[{"def":"Only half alive.","pos":""}],"SEMIVITREOUS":[{"def":"Partially vitreous.","pos":""}],"SEMIVITRIFICATION":[{"def":"The quality or state of being semivitrified.","pos":""},{"def":"A substance imperfectly vitrified.","pos":""}],"SEMIVITRIFIED":[{"def":"Half or imperfectly vitrified; partially converted into glass.","pos":""}],"SEMIVOCAL":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to a semivowel; half cocal; imperfectly sounding.","pos":""}]}